manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Handmade Brass Napkin Rings | Gold | Set of 12 | Napkin Rings - Artisan Crafted in India INCLUDING 12 SETS OF NAPKIN RINGS. EACH NAPKIN RING MEASURES 2.5 INCHES IN OUTER DIAMETER AND 1.5 INCHES IN INNER DIAMETER. FEATURES: MULTI-PURPOSE: Napkin rings are not only for holding napkins but can also be used as a mini flower vase, to hold keys or coins, as a party favor, and more.PREMIUM QUALITY: These napkin rings are made of high-quality brass, which ensures their durability and adds a touch of luxury to your table setting.ELEGANT DESIGN: These napkin rings feature a classic design with a twisted rope pattern that adds an elegant touch to your table decor.VERSATILE: These napkin rings can be used for various occasions, including weddings, parties, banquets, and everyday use, to add a touch of sophistication to your dining experience.DIMENSIONS: Each napkin ring measures 2.5 inches in diameter and 1.5 inch in height.

ABOUT THIS ITEM PACKAGE & COLOR SET OF 12 NAPKIN RINGS THAT ARE GOLD-COLORED AND HAVE BEEN MADE BY HAND IN INDIA. SIZE THE DIAMETER OF EACH RING IS ABOUT 2.5 INCHES (6.4 CM). QUALITY MADE FROM BRASS WITH A POLISHED FINISH. CARE EASY CARE, WIPE CLEAN WITH DAMP SPONGE.

Add a touch of elegance to your table setting with our beautiful brass napkin rings. These exquisite rings are handmade in India by skilled artisans, each one unique and full of character. The intricate designs and high-quality materials make them a stunning addition to any table decor, whether it's for a formal dinner party or a casual gathering. Each napkin ring measures approximately 2.5 inches in diameter and 1.5 inch in height. The set includes 12 rings, enough to adorn all your napkins for a special occasion. These napkin rings are not only beautiful but also functional. They help hold your napkins in place, keeping them neat and tidy for your guests to easily grab. The brass material is durable and long-lasting, ensuring that these rings will be a cherished part of your table setting for years to come.
